  "label": "Verekan Thrice-Bound",
  "description": "This individual is an animated skeleton preserved in a state of ritual desiccation, the light skin tone of bare bone uninterrupted by living flesh. Yellow eyes burn steadily within deep, shadowed sockets, lending a fixed and doctrinal intensity to an otherwise expressionless visage. Gray hair persists in sparse, brittle strands, worn plain and close to the skull, as if retained by lingering sorcery rather than biology. The frame is tall and angular, with long forearms and pronounced joints that emphasize an unyielding, tireless gait typical of the undead of Riftglass Hollow.",
